00:07:54.210 --> 00:07:55.820
I quickly shut the drawer

00:07:55.820 --> 00:07:59.460
and thought was I
storing them incorrectly,

00:07:59.460 --> 00:08:03.260
what was it in the glass
that was causing this,

00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:05.760
how long has this been going on?

00:08:05.760 --> 00:08:10.290
I peeked in and again I
wondered what was I going

00:08:10.290 --> 00:08:11.790
to do about this?

00:08:11.790 --> 00:08:16.490
