01:41:22.650 --> 01:41:24.550
than one millimeter
on the object.

01:41:24.550 --> 01:41:27.720
So it's quite finely restored.

01:41:27.720 --> 01:41:31.530
Another tool we use
is more for geometry.

01:41:31.530 --> 01:41:34.810
The variations in
geometry of the soundbox

01:41:34.810 --> 01:41:37.700
and of the instruments
during the process.

01:41:37.700 --> 01:41:41.990
So this is not a CT scan,

01:41:41.990 --> 01:41:45.530
which is using x-rays,
